videos.headline: Willis dumps off to Keene for TD
videos.description: Ryan Willis throws it short to Dalton Keene who take it 15 yards to end zone.

videos.headline: Canes pick off Hokies deep in their own territory
videos.description: Shaquille Quarterman catches a interception to give Miami good field position.

videos.headline: Langham makes amazing grab with defender draped over him
videos.description: N'Kosi Perry finds Darrell Langham, who makes a tough one-handed catch in the end zone with a defender all over him.

videos.headline: Davis dashes up middle for 42-yard score
videos.description: Cam'Ron Davis takes it up the middle for a 42-yard touchdown to extend Miami's lead to 24-14.

videos.headline: Miami returns punt 51 yards to the house
videos.description: Miami's Jeff Thomas returns a punt 51 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Davis running all over Hokies
videos.description: Cam'Ron Davis sprints down the sideline for his second touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Tempers flare after VT QB is knocked to ground
videos.description: Jhavonte Dean intercepts Ryan Willis' pass and Willis is knocked to the ground with Virginia Tech and Miami players getting into it.
